# Installation a small Debian System

Use the standard installation with the first CD-ROM.

On the list with the installation options uncheck everything with exception of *Standart System Werkzeuge* (*Standard System Utilities*)

After installing the base system do the following:

~~~
sudo apt-get install xorg
sudo apt-get install openbox
~~~

Add the following products

~~~
sudo apt-get install iceweasel
sudo apt-get install mousepad
~~~

## Some commands 

### Stop the system

~~~
sudo shutdown -h now
~~~
